        {
            "id": "block-067",
            "tag": "h2",
            "styles": null,
            "classes": null,
            "text": "Common mistakes to avoid"
        },
        {
            "id": "block-068",
            "tag": "warning",
            "styles": null,
            "classes": null,
            "text": "**Nothing happens when I call a method.** You almost certainly forgot `CharacterUtil.AddCharacter(this)` (or didn't add the `Character` component). Run it once in `OnInit` before anything else."
        },
        {
            "id": "block-069",
            "tag": "warning",
            "styles": null,
            "classes": null,
            "text": "**My character won't respawn / teleport.** `ResetTransform` needs the character's **type** set to **Action**. A plain physics character cannot be repositioned and will fall forever."
        },
        {
            "id": "block-070",
            "tag": "tip",
            "styles": null,
            "classes": null,
            "text": "**Register motions once, not every frame.** Call `AddMotion` in `OnInit`. Calling it repeatedly (for example inside `OnUpdate`) wastes work — `PlayMotion` is the one you call whenever you want the animation to play."
        },
        {
            "id": "block-071",
            "tag": "tip",
            "styles": null,
            "classes": null,
            "text": "**Send `SetInput(this, 0, 0)` to stop.** Movement keeps using the last value you sent, so when the player lets go of the stick, push zeros to bring the character to a halt."
        }
    ]
